    <item>
      <title>Google 强调 AI 搜寻功能让网页获得更高品质点击观看行为、连结查询数量增加，但未提供数据佐证</title>
      <description>&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;针对市场质疑科技业者大幅推广 AI 应用服务，进而造成许多内容网站、部落格等流量&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://mashdigi.com/google-is-again-caught-up-in-eu-antitrust-storm-ai-overviews-infringement-dispute-sparks-dissatisfaction-in-news-publishing-industry/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:大幅减少;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;大幅减少&lt;/a&gt;，市调机构皮尤研究中心 (Pew Research Center) 制作&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2025/07/22/google-users-are-less-likely-to-click-on-links-when-an-ai-summary-appears-in-the-results/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:研究报告;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;研究报告&lt;/a&gt;，指出 Google 搜寻加入&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://mashdigi.com/?s=AI+Overviews" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:AI Overviews 功能;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;AI Overviews 功能&lt;/a&gt;后，对整体网站流量带来明显冲击。不过，Google 搜寻业务负责人 Liz Reid&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://blog.google/products/search/ai-search-driving-more-queries-higher-quality-clicks/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:透过官方部落格回应;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;透过官方部落格回应&lt;/a&gt;，表示搜寻导向网站的流量「相对稳定」，同时使用者点击的「品质更高」，试图为外界对 AI 功能可能损害内容生态的疑虑提出不同观点。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure class="mb-module-gap"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto w-fit"&gt;&lt;img alt="Google 强调 AI 搜寻功能让网页获得更高品质点击观看行为、连结查询数量增加，但未提供数据佐证" class="rounded-lg" loading="lazy" height="515" src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AeB3xo7EFIsKtwZ10sA0oA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUxNQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-08/a1b45c90-73a7-11f0-b74f-39767a981297" width="960" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;figcaption class="text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere" style="max-width:960px"&gt;Google 强调 AI 搜寻功能让网页获得更高品质点击观看行为、连结查询数量增加，但未提供数据佐证&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;Liz Reid 在部落格中表示，AI Overviews 功能推出后，使用者的搜寻行为变得更加频繁，查询内容也趋于复杂与多样化，进一步带动整体点击次数与搜寻品质的提升，强调人们透过 AI Overviews 功能取得解答后，实际上会提出</description>
      <link>https://tw.news.yahoo.com/google-emphasized-that-its-ai-search-function-has-led-to-higher-quality-click-through-rates-and-an-increase-in-link-queries-but-did-not-provide-data-to-support-this-160129014.html</link>
